&lt;h1 id="happiness-is-a-skill-you-can-develop"&gt;Happiness Is a Skill You Can Develop&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feb 3 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;re not stuck at your current level of happiness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first step to increasing your level of happiness is realizing you can. This is where a lot of people get tripped up. For the vast majority of people, some of their happiness—probably a lot more than they think—is in their control.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>